subject: Hockey, Ice
NCAA Ice Hockey Championships
lead_paragraph: Coach David Quinn and 10 freshmen, including Jack Eichel, have helped revive the B.U. men’s hockey team, set for a No. 3 seed in the N.C.A.A. tournament.
